cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.NA, cs.DS, cs.SC 

This paper is about optimizing machine learning problems using distributed-memory parallel implementations of primal and dual block coordinate descent methods. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.NA (Numerical Analysis), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.SC (Supercomputing).
